comment_data.body:
Most of this seems to be redundant with the deallocator code. I'd consider extracting the initial condition into a static methods like the following:
```python
@staticmethod
def generate_freelist_condition(code, type_var, ext_type, size_condition):
    if ext_type.is_final_type:
        ...

# usage:
self.generate_freelist_condition(code, 'Py_TYPE(o)', scope.parent_type, size_condition="> 0")
```

